org.youscope.addon.celldetection

Interface CellVisualizationAddon

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Component, java.rmi.Remote, Resource

    public interface CellVisualizationAddon
extends Resource
    A cell visualization addon is a class supporting to visualize previously detected cells in microscope images by generating new images.

    Moritz Lang
